description:
This is a 6 minute workout called 'Core Strength' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Groove Session and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The The Groove Session vibe means Fun, fluid, expressive, completely in the moment. This is especially good for Days when you want to move intuitively and just vibe. The The Reboot Workout vibe means Deep stretch, low stress, total-body refresh. This is especially good for Recovery days, stress relief, post-travel stiffness..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.

Original workout description: Ignite your core with Pete while listening to 80s music....
